'''Baffle''' was a [[BFL]] labor droid activated at the [[Fondor Shipyards/Legends|Fondor Shipyards]]. He eventually ended up on [[Ruan]] in service to [[Salliche Agricultural Corporation|Salliche Ag]], and was on the verge of being deactivated. Baffle formed a plan for a massive [[Droid/Legends|droid]] [[Droid uprising on Ruan|demonstration]], and was able to put it into effect thanks to help from [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]]. In return, he helped Solo rescue the incarcerated [[Droma]] and locate the destination of the ''[[Trevee]]''.

Han initially mistook Baffle to be [[BLX-5|Bollux]], and became convinced that the two were one and the same. Baffle, however, denied the possibility.

